rth at $ 1 million on a financial disclosure form. But during the campaign he said he had done so in error, based on an inflated appraisal by <PERSON> Sutton </PERSON>. The city Department of Investigation is conducting a separate, previously disclosed investigation into whether <PERSON> Dinkins </PERSON> filed misleading financial disclosure forms regarding the stock.
