<HEAD>New Government Draws Immediate Fire From Opposition</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: SUBS one graf for graf 9 pvs `The Cabinet...' to CORRECT spelling
of last name of Johanes; pickup graf 10 pvs `The Civil....' SUBS one graf
